DESC:The first official world for the Spycraft game line rips back the shroud of conspiracy that has concealed the truth for fifty years, and presents a thrilling setting of incredible movie action, psychic spies, mystic artifacts, and world-spanning villain organizations, threatening to topple the global order. New options! New gadgets! New villains! Shadowforce Archer presents dozens of new and unique options for agents (including chemical monsters, psionic investigators, and mystic spies), as well as gadgets only the Archer Foundation fields, and a host of villains who wish to bring them down.
